<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I think it would be handy to be able to add custom messages (not "error messages") to forms and form elements. This could be used to add "success" messages to display using a decorator / view helper combination at the appropriate position in the form markup.</p>

<p>Just a thought.</p>

